        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #2980b9;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about-section {
            padding: 80px 100px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 2s ease-out;
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 60%;
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 35%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Core Values Section */
        .core-values {
            padding: 50px 100px;
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            display: flex;
            gap:20px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-out;
        }

        .core-value {
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .core-value:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .core-value h3 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .core-value p {
            color: #34495e;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        /* Team Section */
        .team-section {
            padding: 80px 100px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            animation: fadeInUp 2.5s ease-out;
        }

        .team-member {
            flex: 0 1 calc(33.33% - 20px);
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .team-member h4 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Footer Section */
       /* footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1em;
        }*/

        /* Animations */
        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(50px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-section {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .about-text,
            .about-image {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .core-values {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .team-member {
                flex: 0 1 calc(50% - 20px);
            }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 480px) {
            .team-member {
                flex: 0 1 100%;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <h1>About Altura Sphere Technologies</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="about-text">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>At Altura Sphere Technologies, our mission is to shape the future of learning through innovative and interactive e-learning solutions. We aim to empower individuals and organizations to enhance their skills and knowledge to succeed in today's fast-paced digital world. With a focus on personalized learning experiences, we provide a platform that combines cutting-edge technologies with user-friendly interfaces, making learning engaging and effective.</p>
            <p>Whether you're a student, professional, or organization, Altura Sphere Technologies provides the resources and tools to help you excel in your career. We offer a wide range of courses, certifications, and hands-on projects to ensure that our learners are industry-ready.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
